{"tid":1745272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「證據」我相信Simon 無叫雞","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:11:10.000Z","uid":229185,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b357005225cfed9fb62d47b7c4fa03f0ae2bfa55","tid":1745272,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:40:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191122&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60295331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191122%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60295331&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyli3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=8235c7d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191122%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60295331&h=873fae9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191122&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60295331</a><br />\n鄭文傑「幫襯」的按摩場所真的是「邪骨店」嗎？自有關閉路電視畫面曝光後，不少網民從內部裝潢發現，涉事場所應是「麗水雲間休閒會所」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-rubs1qRyOM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-rubs1qRyOM&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyli3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=d1d5a25b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-rubs1qRyOM</a><br />\n<br />\n8月8日 18時42分 入會所<br />\n8月8日 18時 54分入房<br />\n8月8日 21時03分 出會所<br />\n<br />\n（<strong></strong>雙鐘按摩計算，注意到simon沖涼好快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後由東門搵內地示威者父母<br />\n<br />\n有報導話佢係搭高鐵返香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88jkppr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88jkppr.jpg&h=c94495ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然趕啲， 但係21時03分到 23時59時都可<br />\n以見完人之後再趕到深圳北站搭高鐵<br />\n<br />\n根據呢個大陸高鐵網： <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53oEEZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53oEEZV.jpg&h=3107a479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由深圳北去西九龍尾班車係22：27<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ctrip.com/webapp/train/v2/index?page=list&amp;dstationname=%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8C%97&amp;astationname=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;ddate=2019-11-24&amp;popup=close&amp;hiderecommapp=1&amp;allianceid=784552&amp;sid=1341860&amp;openapp=3#/list?VNK=877937bf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ctrip.com%2Fwebapp%2Ftrain%2Fv2%2Findex%3Fpage%3Dlist%26dstationname%3D%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E5%258C%2597%26astationname%3D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%26ddate%3D2019-11-24%26popup%3Dclose%26hiderecommapp%3D1%26allianceid%3D784552%26sid%3D1341860%26openapp%3D3%23%2Flist%3FVNK%3D877937bf&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyli3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=3c33c747\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ctrip.com/webapp/train/v2/index?page=list&amp;dstationname=%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8C%97&amp;astationname=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;ddate=2019-11-24&amp;popup=close&amp;hiderecommapp=1&amp;allianceid=784552&amp;sid=1341860&amp;openapp=3#/list?VNK=877937bf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n21：03由東門去到22：27到深圳北係絕對有可能<br />\n<br />\n（可能你會問， 點解Simon 唔去羅湖過關？）<br />\n<br />\n原因的可能性：<br />\n1.我諗因為公司公幹所以搭高鐵有得claim <br />\n2. 我諗Simon想就返內地示威者的父母而去深圳北<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1607743faeb2bd78c76b0b929c91f33ab84d101f","tid":1745272,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"ca0b77750eb36ea1a942e190c1b013f11f5bc8b3","tid":1745272,"uid":49699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"咁講, SIMON係條訪問到都避而不談自己有無叫雞, 如果無佢實大大聲否認, 但佢只係話呢個唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n但問題係就算佢有叫過雞都唔代表要受如此對待<br />\n<br />\n同埋過關先拉擺明係有政治原因係背後....."},{"pid":"5a952a09c846b71202a39496b8455f85e09218a7","tid":1745272,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"正如訪問所講<br />\n有冇叫雞根本唔係重點<br />\n最重要係受到不人道待遇<br />\n俾中共帶咗去講叫雞問題 完全中晒伏"},{"pid":"b06ec7f295a89